('ONET-PENETRATION_TESTERS', 'source_onet_penetration_testers', 'Penetration Testers', 'Penetration Testers is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Evaluate network system security by conducting simulated internal and external cyberattacks using adversary tools and techniques. Attempt to breach and exploit critical systems and gain access to sensitive information to assess system security.', ARRAY['Application Security Assessor','Application Security Hacker','Application Security Tester','Certified Hacker','Certified Tester','Consulting Advisory Tester','Cyber Analyst','Cyber Assessment Tester','Cyber Assessor','Cyber Security Engineer','Cyber Security Tester','Cyber Tester','Cybersecurity Engineer (Cyber Engineer)','Cybersecurity Specialist','Embedded Tester','Ethical Hacker','Forensic Analysis Tester','Hacker','Hardware Hacker','Information Security Analyst','Information Security Assessor','IT Security Tester (Information Technology Security Tester)','Network Exploitation Analyst','Network Security Engineer','Network Security Tester','Offensive Security Engineer','Penetration Tester','Penetration Testing Consultant','Risk Tester','Security Application Tester','Security Architect','Security Assessment Tester','Security Automation Tester','Security Consultant','Security Consulting Tester','Security Control Assessor','Security Engineer','Security Tester','Systems Security Tester','Tester','Vulnerability Analyst','Vulnerability Assessment Analyst','Vulnerability Management Analyst','Vulnerability Management Engineer','Vulnerability Researcher']::text[], ARRAY['Penetration Testers','Application Security Assessor','Application Security Hacker','Application Security Tester','Certified Hacker','Certified Tester','Consulting Advisory Tester','Cyber Analyst','Cyber Assessment Tester','Cyber Assessor','Cyber Security Engineer','Cyber Security Tester','Cyber Tester','Cybersecurity Engineer (Cybe