('ONET-DIGITAL_FORENSICS_ANALYSTS', 'source_onet_digital_forensics_analysts', 'Digital Forensics Analysts', 'Digital Forensics Analysts is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Conduct investigations on computer-based crimes establishing documentary or physical evidence, such as digital media and logs associated with cyber intrusion incidents. Analyze digital evidence and investigate computer security incidents to derive information in support of system and network vulnerability mitigation. Preserve and present computer-related evidence in support of criminal, fraud, counterintelligence, or law enforcement investigations.', ARRAY['Cyber Analyst','Cyber Defense Analyst','Cyber Digital Forensics','Cyber Digital Media Analyst','Cyber Forensics Analyst','Cyber Intelligence Analyst','Cyber Threat Analyst','Cyber Threat Hunter','Cyber Threat Intelligence Analyst','Cybersecurity Analyst (Cyber)','Cybersecurity Engineer (Cyber)','Cybersecurity Incident Response Analyst (Cyber)','Cybersecurity Specialist (Cyber)','Digital Analyst','Digital Computer Analyst','Digital Cyber Analyst','Digital Forensic Analyst','Digital Forensic Examiner','Digital Forensics Analyst','Digital Investigator','Digital Media Analyst','Incident Responder','Incident Response Analyst','Information Technology Security Analyst (IT Security Analyst)','Insider Threat Analyst','IT Analyst (Information Technology Analyst)','Law Enforcement Counterintelligence Forensics Analyst','Legal Digital Analyst','Malware Analyst','Offensive Security Engineer','Operations Analyst','Security Analyst','Threat Analyst','Threat Intelligence Analyst','Threat Researcher']::text[], ARRAY['Digital Forensics Analysts','Cyber Analyst','Cyber Defense Analyst','Cyber Digital Forensics','Cyber Digital Media Analyst','Cyber Forensics Analyst','Cyber Intelligence Analyst','Cyber Threat Analyst','Cyber Threat Hunter','Cyber Threat Intelligence Analyst','Cyb